  "subject": "Fix role assignment in user creation",
  "commit_message": "Fix role assignment in user creation\n\n- adjust filter in user creation page to display roles\n  starting with `portal_`\n- restart wiremock container when running npm run start:e2e\n  to ensure latest stubs are loaded\n- describe how run e2e tests in the README\n- hard code credentials in auth.setup.ts since they are anyways\n  defined in the onap-realm.yaml that is contained in this repo\n\nIssue-ID: PORTALNG-162\nChange-Id: Ib1d058213ac8446b776f8af8cf681f763b7551d7\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
